listing_company_name: First National Real Estate Collective - Narellan
description:
This absolutely stunning, 45SQ, Metricon property is soon to become the “forever home” of one very lucky family. With a floorplan that has been specifically designed to maximise the amount of natural light, an elegant colour palate and the liberal use of quality materials, this home effortlessly combines “display home” appeal with a genuine “livability”. Very few homes make an impression like this one.


The following is a list of some of the features offered by this amazing property:
- Striking custom façade featuring a second storey balcony and the tasteful incorporation of cladding and render.

- 4 oversized bedrooms
- Master bedroom with private balcony overlooking the “Dancerwood” precinct, separate retreat, stunning ensuite & “his” + “her” walk-in robes (fitted out)
- Ensuite to main complete with under floor heating, free standing bath, custom floating cabinetry with stone top, floor to ceiling tiling, marble floor tiling, oversized shower, frameless shower screen, black tapware & “barn door” feature

- Bedroom 2 + 3 with walk in robes + ceiling fans
- Bedroom 4 with mirrored built-in robe + ceiling fan
- Generous formal lounge / living area at the front of the home
- Practical “mud” room / storage area discreetly positioned at the front door entry.
- The stunning gourmet kitchen is a truly the “heart” of this home. Featuring an oversized island bench with 40mm stone, elegant subway tiled splashback, 900mm cooktop, rangehood, soft close cabinetry, feature pendant lighting, + large walk-in butler’s pantry.
- Butler’s pantry with window splashback feature, separate sink + extensive storage
- Combined lounge + dining area off the kitchen features custom cabinetry + provision for a gas fireplace
- Stackable sliding doors open onto the alfresco area
- Separate media room
- Generous upstairs rumpus area with balcony access
- Main bathroom features custom floating cabinetry with stone top, floor to ceiling tiling, feature floor tiling, frameless shower screen & brushed nickel tapware
- Downstairs powder room with floating vanity, 20mm stone top, feature floor tiling & black tapware

- Oversized laundry with stone bench, extensive custom cabinetry & glass feature entry door
- Large walk-in linen press
- Stunning timber look tiling throughout high traffic areas downstairs
- Custom 2340mm internal doors

- Down lights throughout
- Ducted air conditioning
- Alfresco entertaining area with ceiling fan + downlights
- Remote oversized double garage

- Double gate side access next to the garage
- Fully landscaped 736m2 block

- DA for a pool


Located 900m from Macarthur Anglican school, 1500m from Harrington Park Plaza & 2.5km from the Narellan Town Centre, this property is close to every facility you could possibly need, while still offering the privacy of a quiet side street.


Harrington Grove is a master planned community which is part of the Harrington Park estate. Offering facilities such as a 3 country clubs, multiple function facilities, multiple swimming pools, tennis courts & gym facilities as well as major shopping centre (Coles, medical centre, dentist + assorted specialty options), less than 14km to the new Badgery’s Creek Airport development, multiple child care options, easy access to Narellan, with stunning tree lined streets & extensive parkland and recreation spaces, this is an area which is increasingly desirable.

The team here at First National Collective are very proud to be able to bring this property to the market. We have absolutely no doubt that this will be a much loved home for many years to come.
